text: Hillary Clinton rips GOP senators over their response to the Senate's Russia report: "I don't understand what has happened to the people that I served with, I worked with, I traveled with, who literally seem to have had like a lobotomy or something." https://t.co/hUnClHRDWP

name: axios
text:
California Gov. Gavin Newsom addresses DNC from site of wildfires:

"The hots are getting hotter, the drys are getting drier. Climate change is real. If you are in denial about climate change, come to California." https://t.co/GvGaZVnTYE
